    public interface NameTag
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable
    A representation of the model object 'Name Tag'. This is the base class for all elements in a network container. Id is for identification purpose. For each type of element, id has to be unique. Name and desc are optional. Status is for turning a element on/off. It is serializable for cache implementation.

    The following features are supported:

    • Id
    • Name
    • Desc
    • Number
    • Status
    See Also:
    NetPackage.getNameTag()
